RemoteMatchingMetaData.Formula:
CONCATENATE(
"What (if anything) of the content being validated is in the app/features listed below, & if mentioned, what are they called? (ie\"due dates\" are AKA \"deadlines\"). Present/Missing/Different Name (i.e. AKA):",

ARRAYJOIN(IdeaFeatureNames,", "),

"\n\nFormat your response like this:\n",
"{  \"Features\": [\"Durations\",Statuses\",...],\n  \"Keywords\": [{  \"Keyword Name\": \"priorities\",\n  \"IsMissing\": true (if true),\n  \"AKA\": \"priority levels\" (if diff.)\n },...]\n\n",

"FULL Example: {\n \"Features\":[\"Feature xyz\", \"Feature ...\",...],\n \"Keywords\": [{\"KeywordName\": \"",

ARRAYJOIN(IdeaFeatureNames,"\", IsMissing?, AKA? },\n{\"KeywordName\": \""),

"\", IsMissing?, AKA? }]"
)
